author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall inside corner tips…I have to finish this corner but there’s a divot in the drywall. No problem, I fill it with setting-type joint compound and use a Strait-Flex corner that’s more rigid than paper tape. In fact, I use these corners in every bathroom remodel because they’re strong and make inside corners super easy. For more drywall and bathroom renovation tips visit https://homerepairtutor.com 🔥#drywall #bathroomremodel #diy #homerepairtutor
